Name: SPECIAL REASON RELATED TO MOVEMENT NOTIFICATION
SPECIAL REASON RELATED TO RELEASED STATUS
CAUSE OF FAILURE
Explanation: IN THE CONTEXT OF CAPTURED EQUIPMENT REPORTING THIS FIELD GIVES THE REASON WHY AN EQUIPMENT COULD BE CAPTURED.

Name: REASON MISSION ABORTED
Explanation: THE REASON THAT CAUSED A SCHEDULED MISSION NOT TO HAVE BEEN EXECUTED.

Name: NON RELEASE REASON
Explanation: THE REASON ORDNANCE WAS NOT RELEASED ON TASKED TARGET.

Name: MISSED TARGET REASON
Explanation: THE REASON TASKED TARGET WAS MISSED AFTER ORDNANCE RELEASE.
